4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with in-demand skills in JavaScript and Python. Over 18 weeks, participants gain experience in web development, algorithm scripting, and building applications using front-end libraries and APIs. Classes run three times a week with a low student-to-instructor ratio of 7:1. The program is beginner-friendly; no prior coding experience is required. Upon completion, students receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate. Instruction is available in English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop